{"tid":1690471,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"除左和理非同勇武呢兩大支柱 黃色經濟圈將會成為第三大支柱","createTime":"2019-11-03T10:37:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-04T11:48:51.000Z","uid":129644,"like":28,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"1ec43e7e861b27a106d0ced769e2ebd1d70793eb","tid":1690471,"uid":129644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T10:37:21.000Z","msg":"五個月了 我地仲係苦苦堅持緊<br />\n和理非同勇武都去到一個樽頸位 短期內都見唔到突破既可能性<br />\n<br />\n係呢個時刻 黃色經濟圈就係下個可以升級既地方<br />\n<br />\n因為香港從來都係經濟主導既地方<br />\n<br />\n只有掌握經濟命脈我地先可以真正咁贏<br />\n<br />\n呢個唔係一兩個月就可以見到成效既野<br />\n<br />\n可能要一兩年先會初見成效<br />\n<br />\n但呢個將會係最大既武器<br />\n<br />\n當有第一個黃色既大企業出現既時候<br />\n<br />\n我地就會真正見到勝利既曙光<br />\n<br />\n因為我地將會開始去掌握香港真正既話語權<br />\n<br />\n由今日開始<br />\n<br />\n你我做起 <br />\n<br />\n逢藍必罷<br />\n<br />\n擇黃而買"},{"pid":"66083a44a84cbfaf61be5940904c7e239f0f9221","tid":1690471,"uid":129644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T10:45:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6913102cec29d59dea4bd07205f9812f41731b8f","tid":1690471,"uid":129644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T10:45:44.000Z","msg":"輕輕一推"},{"pid":"df16530efe14ec10f5ad4b18a67af6021de37e01","tid":1690471,"uid":55955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T10:47:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fcbe7af53b475fa50193b1f1847449d8f45099f","tid":1690471,"uid":226984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T10:49:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ad2fac9522ae5d79398f00924f76ef1f2a53f6f","tid":1690471,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T10:49:14.000Z","msg":"1823"},{"pid":"1cb0f5862b2e501642c874f2db68b998b525a7f8","tid":1690471,"uid":103960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T10:49:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"14e0207be1ae7ff4c7b04800441d170673be0656",